dc_description_s: Cartographic Details: Scale approximately 1:1,014,000. 1 in. = 16 mi. or 26 km. (W 97°--W 90°/N 49°--N 43°). Railroad depots and electric lines plotted in red over map showing county boundaries and locations and "relative importance" by type size of cities and towns. Insets: N.E. corner of Minnesota showing Cook Co. -- Minneapolis, St. Paul and vicinity. On verso: indices and statement from the Minnesota State Board of Immigration on opportunities in MN.; Scale approximately 1:1,014,000
